      <title>Hygenco 称印度绿色氢气价格开始下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/green-hydrogen-can-be-cheaper-than-gray-in-india-hygenco-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据印度一家生产商称，利用可再生能源生产的氢气售价开始低于在印度用天然气生产的氢气。]]></description>
